N. diversity, irregularity, unevenness
multiformity &c.
unconformity &c.
roughness &c.
dissimilarity, dissimilitude, divarication, divergence. Adj. diversified varied, irregular, uneven, rough &c.
multifarious
multiform &c.
of various kinds
all manner of, all sorts of, all kinds of. Adv. variously, in all manner of ways, here there and everywhere.
